comment: The Yoneda Lemma. The Yoneda embedding, the curried Hom functor, is full and faithful, and hence is a representation of the category ` C ` as a full subcategory of the category ` Q ` of presheaves on ` C ` . (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 29-Jan-2017.)
